                Neptun<supplied reason="lost">o <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>sacrum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Sicinius Coeli<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">nus</supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Paccius Matu<supplied reason="lost">rus</supplied> <lb n="5"/>IIIIviri <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> qu<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>inq</abbr><ex>uennales</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/>ex stilaris
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Formular ex stilaris bisher noch nicht bezeugt; entweder Äquivalent für ex decreto decurionum, ex senatus sententia oder ex usuris, ex sportulis, ex aere collato.</p>
